INSERT INTO `weekly_plan_tasks` VALUES (1,1,'monday','Meeting World Faire trade organization and finalizing training for them','a meeting with the WFTO about a bespoke climate change and environmental protection training they require.','2025-07-28','high','pending','2025-07-28 07:53:09','2025-07-28 07:53:09',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(7,2,'monday','Update LMS and Create SMME certificate','Project Management Course Administration:\r\n\r\nUpload the recorded session from the previous week to the appropriate section on the Learning Management System (LMS) under the Project Management course.\r\n\r\nAccess the Google Form responses for both learner attendance and lesson evaluation. Extract and organize this data into a structured format within a spreadsheet for record-keeping and reporting purposes.\r\n\r\nSMME Certification:\r\n\r\nPrepare and finalize participation certificates for the SMME training attendees. Ensure accuracy of names, training titles, and dates.\r\n\r\nPrint the certificates professionally at MinuteManPress to ensure quality and readiness for distribution.','2025-07-28','medium','pending','2025-07-28 08:52:12','2025-07-28 08:52:12',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,2,'tuesday','RFA Training Facilitator Workshop','Will be introduced to the core concepts, strategies, and tools required to effectively facilitate RFA modules on responsible fisheries practices.','2025-07-29','medium','pending','2025-07-28 08:52:12','2025-07-28 08:52:12',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(9,2,'wednesday','RFA Training Facilitator Workshop','Will be introduced to the core concepts, strategies, and tools required to effectively facilitate RFA modules on responsible fisheries practices.\r\n\r\nBe on standby at 18:00 for technical assistance on Project Management Course.','2025-07-30','medium','pending','2025-07-28 08:52:12','2025-07-28 08:52:12',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(10,2,'thursday','RFA Training Facilitator Workshop','Will have the opportunity to put our learning into practice by delivering a training session. This is an essential part of the certification process, as will be required to demonstrate our ability to facilitate and engage participants.','2025-07-31','medium','pending','2025-07-28 08:52:12','2025-07-28 08:52:12',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(11,2,'friday','Strip Test the Exam Assessment Tab on LMS','The assessment incorporates key features aligned with QCTO requirements and best practices for secure, inclusive, and scalable online evaluation. The following activities are scheduled for testing starting Friday:\r\n1.	Feature Testing and Quality Assurance:\r\nConduct comprehensive testing of all implemented assessment features, including but not limited to:\r\n1. Secure Online Assessment Environment\r\n2. QCTO-Compliant Assessment Types\r\n3. Assessment Integrity and Security\r\n4. Accessibility and User Inclusivity\r\n5. Real-Time Monitoring and Reporting\r\n6. System Integration and Data Security\r\n7. Candidate Support Mechanisms\r\n8. Post-Assessment Workflow\r\n9. System Scalability and Performance\r\n2.	Bug Identification and Resolution:\r\no	Document any detected bugs or system inconsistencies during testing.\r\no	Propose evidence-based solutions or recommendations to address the identified issues, supported by relevant research and best practices in digital assessments.','2025-08-01','high','pending','2025-07-28 08:52:12','2025-07-28 08:52:12',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(12,3,'monday','Finalize the Final Integrated Summative Assessment (FISA) Instrument and Marking Memorandum, ensuring compliance with QCTO requirements, before submission.','-Review FISA for cohort 1 developed by Sol and ensure that it meets QCTO requirements\r\n-Finalize FISA instrument & memo for cohort 2\r\n-Ensure both documents are aligned and meet QCTO\'s criteria\r\n-Submit to QCTO','2025-07-28','high','pending','2025-07-28 13:16:10','2025-07-28 13:16:10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(13,3,'monday','finalize Examiner/ Developer Reports that meet QCTO standards, ensuring they are aligned with the Final Integrated Summative Assessment (FISA) instruments and accurately reflect assessment outcomes.','- Ensure assessments align with the occupational qualification outcomes and associated curriculum components\r\n- Compliance to standards set for programme Exit Level Outcome\r\n- Compile detailed Examiner Reports for each summative assessment conducted','2025-07-28','high','pending','2025-07-28 13:16:10','2025-07-28 13:16:10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(14,3,'tuesday','Tuesday to Thursday: Attend 3-Day WWF RFA Facilitator Training Workshop','This training is designed to build capacity in sustainable fisheries facilitation. The goal is to prepare participants lead dialogues and workshops that support sustainable marine resource management.','2025-07-29','high','pending','2025-07-28 13:16:10','2025-07-28 13:16:10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(15,3,'friday','Prepare Eco Ranger Files for Evaluation & Monitoring','Com[pile and update all the relevant Eco Ranger SP documentation in preparing for an upcoming evaluation and monitoring. This includes ensuring that participant records, activity reports, attendance registers, training materials and supporting evidence (e.g, photos, feedback forms & learner docs) are complete, accurate.','2025-08-01','high','pending','2025-07-28 13:16:10','2025-07-28 13:16:10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(16,4,'monday','Update LMS and google sheets links for PM Class','Update all LMS and Google Sheets links for the Project Management class to ensure accurate access for students and instructors, particularly for last Wednesday’s session attendance and course evaluation. Confirm data is correctly captured in Google Sheets for reporting. Additionally, design a comprehensive pre-course survey for the upcoming PM cohort to assess incoming knowledge, experience with project management (including certifications like PMP, CAPM, Agile), familiarity with tools (e.g., MS Project, Trello), professional background, learning goals, and preferred learning styles. The survey will inform course customization, enabling tailored content delivery, improved pacing, and a more personalized, effective learning experience aligned with student needs.','2025-08-04','medium','pending','2025-08-04 07:42:29','2025-08-04 07:42:29',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(17,4,'tuesday','Prepare for the PM first assessment','I wil be preparing for the first online Project Management assessment on the LMS by reviewing and updating uploaded materials to improve instructions, formatting, question clarity, and alignment with QCTO standards, with all revisions to be completed by 6:00 PM Tuesday. Concurrently, I am ensuring the instructor, assessor, and moderator have correct LMS access and verified roles, while testing submission and grading workflows to guarantee a smooth, error-free evaluation process and timely feedback delivery.','2025-08-05','high','pending','2025-08-04 07:42:29','2025-08-04 07:42:29',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(18,4,'wednesday','Continue updating the LMS Exam tab','I will enhance the LMS Exam tab to meet academic and QCTO standards by strengthening security through authentication, session monitoring, timed access, randomized questions, and plagiarism detection. Controlled navigation and proctoring options will help ensure assessment integrity. The interface is being optimized for accessibility with improved screen reader compatibility, color contrast, font readability, and support for alternative input methods, promoting inclusivity for learners with disabilities. The goal is to create a secure, fair, and user-friendly evaluation process that reflects real-world project management practices and accommodates diverse needs.','2025-08-06','medium','pending','2025-08-04 07:42:29','2025-08-04 07:42:29',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(19,4,'thursday','Continue updating the LMS Exam tab','I will enhance the LMS Exam section to ensure a secure, efficient, and learner-centered assessment process. Key upgrades inc